Game information:  


Mitsurugi Kamui Hikae - action game in which you control the girls,
masterfully owning knives. Battles take place on a small stage,
and only the speed and elegance of your actions can bring you victory.
Improve your skills and abilities, and be ready for battle with the bosses.
